General.Name: Marechale Capital Plc
General.Description: Marechale Capital Plc engages in the provision of professional advisory and broking services to companies in the United Kingdom. It offers capital raising services, such as equity financing, mezzanine, and debt financing services. The company also provides advisory services, including strategic review and consultancy, growth capital, and refinancing and exit advice. It serves the hospitality sector. The company was formerly known as St Helen's Capital Plc. Marechale Capital Plc was incorporated in 1998 and is based in London, the United Kingdom.
